Class DOMParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • DOMParser

  • public class DOMParser
extends java.lang.Object
    DOMParser allows us to take an Object representation of an HTML document and extract a frequency distribution. buildFreqDist() allows us to obtain a frequency distribution. getScrapedURLs() allows us to extract out all newly seen URLs we may want to visit later.
